    Mint Geoff 50e18 cWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 cWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 500e8)
    Assert Equal (CToken cWBTC UnderlyingBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e18)
