    Invariant Remains (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance cWBTC) (Exactly 55e18)
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance Root) (Exactly 0e18)
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 cWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 500e8)
